main event: Two unidentified objects were sighted over Duluth, Minnesota in 1966.
interesting points: The objects were observed for about 5 minutes.
The objects appeared as changing red lights.
The objects were observed to move behind and in front of clouds.
The witness was unable to estimate the speed or distance of the objects.
The witness reported the sighting to the U.S. Air Force.
sighted object: two unidentified objects with changing red lights
